Class GanttChartUndoableEdit

java.lang.Object

      dgantt.GanttChartUndoableEdit
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.undo.UndoableEdit
public class GanttChartUndoableEdit
extends javax.swing.undo.AbstractUndoableEdit

An UndoableEdit for recording changes made to a GanttChart and providing the means to undo such changes. Four steps are required: 1) add edited tasks; 2) grab a snapshot of the before states; 3) grab a snapshot of the after states; and 4) commit the changes to the UndoManager.
